abstract_ssm: Robert Levinn attended New York University School of Engineering from 1949 to 1953 and received his Bachelor of Science degree in mechanical engineering. This collection includes a 1949-1950 Palisades Handbook: A Guide to Campus Life for NYU's University Heights campus. A supply list for an E.D.11. class within the College of Engineering is also in this collection.
